---
---

<section class="where section section-cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="where__heading reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Where We're Going</p>
      <h2>The road ahead.</h2>
      <ul class="where__list">
        <li>A California flagship is moving from blueprint to ground.</li>
        <li>An urban network is taking root in Missouri, with two sites in development.</li>
        <li>Routes are being charted across Montana.</li>
        <li><a class="where__nda-link" href="/investors">Qualified investors</a> can review the full pipeline under NDA.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="where__cta reveal">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/investors">
        Request investor briefing
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
          <polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline" href="https://fieldnotes.rangeway.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Subscribe to Field Notes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .where__heading {
    max-width: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 0.65fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(32px, 6vw, 92px);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .where__heading h2 {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .where__heading .eyebrow,
  .where__heading h2 {
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .where__list {
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 1 / span 2;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-strong);
  }

  .where__list li {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-4) clamp(42px, 5vw, 72px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .where__list li::before {
    content: counter(road, decimal-leading-zero);
    counter-increment: road;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: var(--space-4);
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 0;
    background: transparent;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
  }

  .where__list {
    counter-reset: road;
  }

  .where__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .where__nda-link {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .where__nda-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .where__cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-7);
  }

  .where__cta .btn {
    min-width: 17em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .where__heading {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-5);
    }

    .where__list {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
